0:37:31.449,0:37:33.009
You may stay here.

0:37:33.980,0:37:36.349
I thank Your Majesty.

0:37:36.500,0:37:37.840
What is your name?

0:37:38.820,0:37:40.960
My humble name is Yu Ying'er.

